-- RIM Denies Newspaper Report of India E-Mail Agreement, Guardian Reports
-- B y   J o h n   S i m p s o n
-- 2010-12-31T02:51:40Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-31/rim-denies-newspaper-report-of-india-e-mail-deal-guardian-says.html
  Research in Motion Ltd . denied a
report in the Economic Times of India that said it will give the
Indian government access to all messages and e-mails sent by
users of its BlackBerry smartphone in the country, the Guardian
reported, citing a RIM spokesman. The spokesman said the report
“is both false and technologically infeasible,” according to
the newspaper.   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
John Simpson at 
 jsimpson12@bloomberg.net  